--- Instruction ---

[Z] Confirm
[X/Shift] Cancel
[C] Open Inventory
[Escape] Quit
When HP is 0, you lose.
Text-level0-192-m_Text-1: Based on Undertale by Toby Fox and the "Dusttale" AU concept by Osteophile
Text-level0-194-m_Text-1: This mode is for the extreme Undertale player looking for a challenge.
Text-level0-195-m_Text-1: Your save file has been corrupted, and you must restart the game. If this issue is a recurring problem, please reach out to me for support on Gamejolt.
Text-level0-199-m_Text-1: Press Z to change an option.
Text-level0-213-m_Text-1: This is for players who care a little more about the story than about the battles. After every attack in a battle, you will regain the percentage of health you set. Leave it at 0% for a normal Undertale experience.
